it don't matter what speed you burn at. it what kind of dvd-rom you have in your xbox.

your computer will not read a xbox game disk anyway it will burn them but not read them.

thompson dvd-rom reads both dvd-r/+r 
samsaung read dvd-r and not dvd+r
philips will only read dvd-rs

and what brand of dvd are you using.
